        <p>No, Invesco has not announced any changes to the 0.20% expense ratio for QQQ in 2025. It remains stable, just as it was in 2024, providing predictability for long-term investors.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How does the QQQ expense ratio compare to other ETFs?</summary>
