      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What is the difference between QQQ and QQQM fees?</summary>
        <p>QQQ charges a 0.20% expense ratio, while the Invesco NASDAQ 100 ETF (QQQM) charges 0.15%. QQQM was created specifically for buy-and-hold investors looking for a lower-cost way to access the exact same index.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Are ETF expense ratios tax-deductible?</summary>
